t not being able to find the `ogre2` render engine.", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<h1 id=\"markdown-header-summary\">Summary</h1>\n<p>Add ogre 2.1 dependency to CI systems</p>\n<h1 id=\"markdown-header-motivation\">Motivation</h1>\n<p>Some rendering tests are using <code>ogre</code> and we should start switching them to use <code>ogre2</code>. To do this, we need to first add ogre2.1 dependency to our CI systems otherwise the tests will fail with a warning msg about not being able to find the <code>ogre2</code> render engine.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2019-02-27T20:20:21.626798+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2019-02-27T20:20:21.626798+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 14}